    "asOf": "2019-02-11",
    "date": "2019-10-21T15:02:26Z",
    "text": "Banning Lobbying and Safeguarding Trust Act or the BLAST Act\n\nThis bill revises the post-employment lobbying ban on former Members and elected officers of Congress.\n\nSpecifically, it imposes a permanent ban on lobbying contacts by a former Member of the U.S. Senate (currently, a two-year ban), a former Member of the U.S. House of Representatives (currently, a one-year ban), or a former elected officer of the House or Senate (currently, a one-year ban)."
  },
